<h1>Securing Software Licenses</h1>
<p>On this page, you can manage software license security, especially if you keep track of <a href="../../../../alvao-asset-management/software-management/licenses">licenses for multiple organizations</a>.</p>
<p>Options:</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Command Panel</strong>
  <ul>
  <li><strong>Add</strong> - add a new <a href="software-licenses-security/item">license</a> to the list.</li>
  <li><strong>Edit</strong> - edit the selected permission.</li>
  <li><strong>Remove</strong> - irreversibly remove the selected permission.</li>
  </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Permissions table</strong> - contains all permissions of software licenses and their selected attributes. You can <a href="../../../../alvao-asset-management/working-with-tables">customize the table as needed</a>.</li>
</ul>
</asp:Content>
